Class FDv2ProtocolHandler

    • com.launchdarkly.sdk.internal.fdv2.sources.FDv2ProtocolHandler

  • public final class FDv2ProtocolHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements the FDv2 protocol state machine for handling payload communication events. See: FDV2PL-payload-communication specification.
